high_descs: walk to the diningtable
pick up butterknife from the table
walk to a room with an apple on the floor
Cut a piece of apple from inside the box, close box.
walk away from the fridge with the knife
walk to the fridge
Open the refrigerator door, place the apple inside the refrigerator.
Close the refrigerator door and walk into the hallway.
walk to the microwave in the hallway
pick up a piece of apple from the box
bring apple to the sidetable, place apple in the microwave
Take the apple back out of the microwave, and place it on the sidetable in front of the microwave.

Take the butterknife from the table
Go straight turn right to the apple room.
Cut the apple in the box.
Exit from the room go straight then turn left to the fridge.
Put the butterknife in the fridge.
Turn around turn right again turn right to the apple room

high_descs: Head to the diningtable in the front to reach the round table.
Pick up the butterknife from the table.
Turn around and head right to reach the apple box.
Cut the green apple into slices in the box.
Turn left and walk into the room on the left and reach the fridge.
Put the butterknife in the fridge.
Turn around and head right to reach the apple box.
Pick up the green apple slice from the box.
Turn left and walk into the room on the left and reach the microwave.
Heat the green apple slice in the microwave and take the apple out.
Turn to face the sidetable in front of the microwave.
Put the apple slice on the sidetable.
